---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Plumbing Repairs | Berkeley Plumbing — Newbury Park, CA"
  description="Plumbing repairs in Newbury Park and the Conejo Valley. Leak detection, fixture repair, and diagnostics by a C-36 licensed contractor. Upfront pricing. CSLB #1115151."
>

  <!-- Page hero -->
  <section class="bg-navy-900 text-white py-16 lg:py-24 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <a href="/" class="text-copper text-sm hover:text-copper-light mb-6 inline-block">← Back to home</a>
      <p class="text-copper font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Services</p>
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-5">Plumbing Repairs</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-300 text-lg lg:text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
        Leak detection, fixture repair, and plumbing diagnostics. We find the root cause and fix it correctly, not just the visible symptom.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20 px-4 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">

      <div class="lg:col-span-2 prose prose-slate max-w-none">

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-navy-900">Diagnostics First</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          Most plumbing problems have a visible symptom: a wet spot under a cabinet, a slow drain, low pressure at one fixture. The symptom is rarely the full story. Berkeley Plumbing diagnoses before recommending. You'll understand what's wrong, what caused it, and what fixing it actually involves, before any work begins.
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          Upfront pricing means you approve the scope and cost before I pick up a wrench. No surprises at the end of the job.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-navy-900 mt-8">Common Repair Services</h2>

        <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-navy-900 mt-5">Leak Detection and Repair</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-600">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-copper mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Under-slab leak detection</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-copper mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Supply line and shut-off valve repair</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-copper mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Drain line repair and replacement</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-copper mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Pipe corrosion and pinhole leak repair</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-navy-900 mt-5">Fixture Repair and Replacement</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-600">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-copper mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Faucet and valve repair or replacement</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-copper mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Toilet repair: flapper, fill valve, flush valve</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-copper mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Shower valve and cartridge replacement</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-copper mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Garbage disposal installation and repair</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-navy-900 mt-5">Drain Services</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-600">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-copper mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Kitchen and bathroom drain clearing</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-copper mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Main line clearing</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-copper mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Slow drain diagnosis and correction</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-navy-900 mt-5">Pressure and Flow</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-600">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-copper mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Pressure regulator adjustment and replacement</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-copper mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Low pressure diagnosis</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-copper mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Water hammer diagnosis and correction</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="mt-8 bg-copper/5 border border-copper/20 rounded-lg p-5">
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
            <strong class="text-navy-900">Not available for:</strong> Large-scale emergency drain clearing for rental properties or commercial facilities. Berkeley Plumbing focuses on residential repairs where quality of workmanship matters. If your project is a custom home or high-end residential property, this is the right fit.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Sidebar -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-1">
        <div class="bg-stone-warm rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100 sticky top-24">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-4">Request an Estimate</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-5 leading-relaxed">
            Describe the issue and I'll provide upfront pricing before any work begins.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/contact/"
            class="block w-full bg-copper hover:bg-copper-light text-white font-semibold py-3 px-5 rounded text-center transition-colors mb-3"
          >
            Get an Estimate
          </a>
          <a
            href="tel:(310) 733-7808"
            class="block w-full border border-slate-300 hover:border-navy-800 text-slate-700 font-semibold py-3 px-5 rounded text-center transition-colors text-sm"
          >
            Call (310) 733-7808
          </a>
          <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-slate-200 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <p class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-copper" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Diagnostics before repair</p>
            <p class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-copper" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Upfront pricing</p>
            <p class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-copper" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> CSLB #1115151</p>
            <p class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-copper" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Licensed and insured</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Service areas -->
  <section class="py-12 px-4 bg-stone-warm border-t border-slate-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm text-center">
        Plumbing repairs in:
        <a href="/service-areas/newbury-park/" class="text-copper hover:underline">Newbury Park</a>,
        <a href="/service-areas/agoura-hills/" class="text-copper hover:underline">Agoura Hills</a>,
        <a href="/service-areas/thousand-oaks/" class="text-copper hover:underline">Thousand Oaks</a>,
        <a href="/service-areas/westlake-village/" class="text-copper hover:underline">Westlake Village</a>, and
        <a href="/service-areas/calabasas/" class="text-copper hover:underline">Calabasas</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
